## Coupon Request Schema

URL
```
[POST]: https://www.trocafone.local/comprar/checkout/steps/coupons
```

Form Data
```
{
    couponCode: '{{coupon_code}}',
    trocables[]: '{{trocable_id}}',
    _method: 'POST',
    trocable_id: '{{trocable_id}}',
}
```

## Delivery Cost Request Schema

URL
```
[POST]: https://www.trocafone.local/location/delivery-info/{{trocable_id}}?trocableId={{trocable_id}}
```
Form Data
```
{
    _method: '{{GET}}',
}
```
